Simple Calculator 
A Simple Calculator built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. This lightweight web application allows users to perform basic arithmetic operations with a clean and intuitive interface.

Features 
 Perform basic calculations: Addition (+), Subtraction (-), Multiplication (ร), and Division (รท)
 Clear (C) button to reset calculations
 Responsive and user-friendly design
 Lightweight and fast execution

Technologies Used 
HTML - Structure of the calculator
CSS - Styling and layout
JavaScript - Logic for calculations and user interaction
